snippet.title: Party Panic - Xbox One & PS4 Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Available worldwide for purchase Friday, August 21st, 2020! (08/21/2020)
BUY NOW! http://partypanicgame.com
Xbox One: http://partypanicgame.com/xbox
PS4: http://partypanicgame.com/ps4

For more information see the official website: http://partypanicgame.com
Or the steam page where it's already released: http://partypanicgame.com/steam
Follow the official twitter to get updates: http://twitter.com/partypanicgame

Party Panic is a crazy online and local-multiplayer party game. Compete against your friends in 30+ rapid fire minigames, play the Board Game mode, race through the brutal Gauntlet, or complete the trophy challenges on Trophy Island. There is even a built in drinking game! You'll laugh, you'll cry, it's stupid. Grab your friends, pick your characters and get partying in this exciting and panic filled game!

#partygame #newrelease #partypanic #steam #xbox #xboxone #sony #ps4
